"Pandora's Box"(1991)  
  When I Needed You  
  *(Steven Tyler)*  
  
  *Okay, so I know this isn't really an Aerosmith song, per se.*  
  *Nonetheless, it was written by Steven Tyler and it is included in an*  
  *Aerosmith box set. I think those are good enough reasons for putting it in*  
  *the Aerosmith section of OLGA instead of starting a new file for "Chain*  
  *Reaction." Anyway, here it is, like it or not.*  
  
  "I can't ever forget how excited I was about being in an actual recording  
  band. It was a total dream come true. The other side of it is that it's a  
  pretty lame song. I never got a cent. So that was my first taste of  
  'shysterism.'"  
    -Steven Tyler  
  
